high_descs: Turn to the right to go towards the table.  Turn left to face the table.
Pick up the coffee mug that is on the coffee maker.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Put the coffee mug in the sink on the left.  Turn the water on to fill the mug up. Then turn the water off.  Pick up the coffee mug.
Turn around and move towards the table.  Turn left to face the table.
Put the coffee mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Get a mug to make coffee.

high_descs: Turn right and hang right to the far short end of the table.
Pick up the coffee mug in the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the mug off in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the table.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the far end of the white table against the wall.
Pick the mug that is resting in the coffee machine up off the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug in the left sink basin under the faucet, turn on the water until the mug is full, then turn the water off and pick the full mug back up.
Turn around and walk back over to the end of the white table where you got the mug.
Place the filled mug back into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug full of water in the coffee machine.
